				Below, you'll find a visual list of technologies that are the subject of discussion on my blog (it's not an exhaustive list, but it will give you a general idea 
				of what to expect)
				<div class="flex flex-wrap [&>*]:mx-2 [&>*]:my-2 py-4">
					<img width="46" height="46" alt="React" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg"/>
